Class: CacheEntry

CacheEntry

new CacheEntry(value, createdAtopt, lastAccessedAtopt)

Cache entry abstraction A single entry inside a cache

It contains the data as originally returned by Stormpath along with additional metadata like timestamps.

Parameters:
Name Type Attributes Description
value object

value to store in cache
createdAt Date <optional>

time when cache entry created
lastAccessedAt Date <optional>

time when cache entry was last accessed
